Mobile Card Components Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides comprehensive card-based layout components for mobile interfaces.
Includes various card styles, layouts, and interactions optimized for touch interfaces
with material design and iOS-style card patterns.

Key Features:
- Material Design card components
- iOS-style grouped table cards
- Expandable and collapsible cards
- Card stacks and carousels
- Interactive card gestures
- Elevation and shadow effects
- Card-based navigation
- Content cards with media
- Action cards with buttons
- Information cards and dashboards
- Card animations and transitions
- Accessibility support

Provides complete card component system for building modern mobile
interfaces with card-based layouts and interactions.
:End Note

